      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LETHAL AVENGER (3) comes here off a decent win over 435m at this track in 24.47. Rates a top chance again if runs up to latest. DR. ERICA (7) finds it hard to break through. Continues to race well, filling the minors at the last three starts, the latest when third (22.66) at Warragul. Solid record here at the distance winning nine races. Comes through a solid form race last start. Deserves a win and gets her chance. HAMISH ROSE (4) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Mugshot (24.79) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Can feature again. SOMERTON ANN (2) picked up an unexpected cheque last time and is in the mix again.",
